data.description: Come take a look at this beautiful oasis of a home which has high ceilings with floor-to ceiling windows, a large media room, an outside covered patio with a built-in grill, Great for family entertainment! This home has an open concept kitchen opens up to the large great room; it is located in a gated community which has a volley ball court, a pavilion with a basketball court, beauty large community pool and so much more! This home is THE perfect family home! Contact me for a private showing!
